I met Colton Woods through the Blue Tile Obsession. Colton, his father Perry and I exchanged email over the last two years or so...  I met up with them when Colton came in for the AmTec contest at Vans. It was really cool getting to hang out with them and get to know other skaters as we share so much in common. Colton is humble, bright and rips on a skateboard! Recently, we met up in San Jose and had a great time hanging out and talking. Colton rode well in San Jose and I am looking forward to seeing him rip it up in the future. Thank you Perry and Colton for the great conversation, good food and friendship. Thank you to Gage Thompson for the image. Skate- Ozzie

